rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0020
rows.name:
It's a real shame our friend didn't make it,
but at least the mission's complete, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0030
rows.name: Credit where it's due, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0110
rows.name: These lives won't go to waste.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0120
rows.name: Not to rain on your parade here,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0130
rows.name: but how are we doing with the Ares?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0140
rows.name: We're making good progress, thanks to you, aren't we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0150
rows.name:
We have some news, so would you mind stopping
by the restricted hangar after this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs32150100_MSG0170
rows.name: It wasn't easy, but the mission was a success.[ST:wait ]
